  <front>
   <head>Epigrammi - III. Se fidem servaturum.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Si post fata novos animas errare per artus,</l>
     <l n="2">Vera docent Samii dogmata nota Senis;</l>
     <l n="3">Nec pote mens eadem mutari, seu ferus altis</l>
     <l n="4">Erret aper silvis, seu vaga cantet avis:</l>
     <l n="5">Ipse ego, mens quoniam est uni servire puellae,</l>
     <l n="6">Exsurgam moestis turtur ab exsequiis.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
